Ecoair International bụ ụlọ ọrụ ụgbọ elu dị na Algiers, n’ obodo Algeria, nke e guzobere na afo 1999
N'afọ 2002, e jikọtara ya na Khalifa Group, ụlọ ọrụ nne na nna nke Khalifa Airways
Na-arụ ọrụ site na ọdụ ụgbọ elu Houari Boumedienne, Ecoair International nyere ụgbọ elu na Europ, gụnyere Brussels-Charleroi ya na North Afrika, na n'ime obodo  Algeria.
E guzobere Ecoair International na afo 1999 wee malite ọrụ site n'enyemaka nke Khalifa Airways ya na Khalifa Group.
